l class="tocchild" id="tocchild1859360"></ul></li><li data-ref="1859366"><div class="toclinkname"><i class="material-icons toclink" data-ref="1859366" data-open="" data-queried="">&#58133;</i><a href="../2025.1.9_9197/?source=Help&amp;id=getting_to_know_schematic_view">Getting to know the Schematic View</a><i style="display:none;" class="material-icons tocbookmark" data-ref="1859366"></i></div><ul class="tocchild" id="tocchild1859366"></ul></li><li data-ref="1859368"><div class="toclinkname"><i class="material-icons toclink" data-ref="1859368" data-open="" data-queried="">&#58133;</i><a href="../2025.1.9_9197/?source=Help&amp;id=getting_to_know_graph_view">Getting to know the graph view</a><i style="display:none;" class="material-icons tocbookmark" data-ref="1859368"></i></div><ul class="tocchild" id="tocchild1859368"></ul></li><li data-ref="1859373"><div class="toclinkname"><i class="material-icons toclink" data-ref="1859373" data-open="" data-queried="">&#58133;</i><a href="../2025.1.9_9197/?source=Help&amp;id=getting_to_know_timeline">Getting to know the timeline</a><i style="display:none;" class="material-icons tocbookmark" data-ref="1859373"></i></div><ul class="tocchild" id="tocchild1859373"></ul></li><li data-ref="1859377"><div class="toclinkname"><i class="material-icons toclink" data-ref="1859377" data-open="" data-queried="">&#58133;</i><a href="../2025.1.9_9197/?source=Help&amp;id=working_with_object_tabs">Working with Object Tabs and Object Tab Groups</a><i style="display:none;" class="material-icons tocbookmark" data-ref="1859377"></i></div><ul class="tocchild" id="tocchild1859377"></ul></li><li data-ref="1859388"><div class="toclinkname"><i class="material-icons toclink" data-ref="1859388" data-open="" data-queried="">&#58133;</i><a href="../2025.1.9_9197/?source=Help&amp;id=getting_to_know_media_pool">Working with the Media Pool</a><i style="display:none;" class="material-icons tocbookmark" data-ref="1859388"></i></div><ul class="tocchild" id="tocchil